{"tid":403990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟睇古裝劇啲士兵心口係咩字？","createTime":"2017-09-17T15:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T05:36:22.000Z","uid":2104,"like":753,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b694aee3d691232c53ce948c4f7cac7c9c4e35","tid":403990,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"睇古裝劇果陣如果有士兵<br />\n咁佢地件戲服係一件古裝士兵衫<br />\n件衫喺心口前面有個大圈圈<br />\n我明明記得團團入面係大大個兵字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/233332_34b6f1b154cfb5913836bfb24e7f23a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F233332_34b6f1b154cfb5913836bfb24e7f23a5.jpg&h=3bbe79d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我朋友死都話係個卒字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/233410_faab27433050d7596b24a4d8cc56bbee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F233410_faab27433050d7596b24a4d8cc56bbee.jpg&h=469d4494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地拗咗好耐 跟住走去問我女朋友<br />\n佢就話好似係個清字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/233515_9fa1c86c647ca53e45819f1b99f0671b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F233515_9fa1c86c647ca53e45819f1b99f0671b.jpg&h=bd9f5e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我好亂...<br />\n拿拿臨打去問我個妹<br />\n問佢記唔記得應該係咩字<br />\n我頂佢竟然話係個勇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/233713_44958d9de6b6349705c3d84e24946faf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F233713_44958d9de6b6349705c3d84e24946faf.jpg&h=045cd17b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我頂！！！<br />\n而家我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地四個都記得係唔同嘅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n越攪越亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5065e839a62f438187391d48f2d68425ff1834f9","tid":403990,"uid":7764,"like":16,"dislike":195,"score":-179,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"記錯晒啦，係個柒字"},{"pid":"e02aab5d77208a1142787fa5757e24b7146b6b4d","tid":403990,"uid":78222,"like":6,"dislike":188,"score":-182,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"你咁樣我好尷尬架喎"},{"pid":"5cc467f73aee7af045dbea202ceb86445d2418f0","tid":403990,"uid":69947,"like":686,"dislike":9,"score":677,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"四隻字都有，<br />\n依舖打和啦，<br />\nSuper!!!!"},{"pid":"68d59eeeb685c57bebc3396d403bcf0f1ea53b3d","tid":403990,"uid":86249,"like":29,"dislike":39,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"曼鳩拉效應"},{"pid":"1829edd9f8aa0172d44043f7e7f6a01746c4fd5b","tid":403990,"uid":660,"like":19,"dislike":33,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼鳩拉效應</blockquote><br />\n曼德斯鳩效應呀"},{"pid":"9b6342653b944a7bf027359108a52b5d37f87703","tid":403990,"uid":953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"死字"},{"pid":"1bd40fe4c1cc5869a5ccf6a1c43f2dc71c91a4fb","tid":403990,"uid":2104,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記錯晒啦，係個柒字</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/235417_bc635510dea7485cbcc8e2038e7e9374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F0